0.8.1.name: wordpress/afc-google-map
0.8.1.description:
NOTE: This plugin is depreciated now, so development is discontinued. Instead of current plugin, users are advised to use more feature-rich and up to date Umapper plugin - it has everything AFC Google Map offered, plus many new features.

The AFC Google Map plugin provides easy map navigation and displays geographical locations with your markers, polylines, polygons and layers. This component uses Google Map Data by connecting to Google Maps API.

One of the most important features of this plugin is the KML support. It fully supports KML standards, plus allows you to create simple Placemarks KML files on-fly.

Plugin uses WordPress quicktag for map object addition, so this procedure is as simple as it could be.
